Class NumberParmBehaviorUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.fhir.persistence.jdbc.util.type.NumberParmBehaviorUtil
  • public class NumberParmBehaviorUtil
extends Object
    Number Parameter Behavior Util encapsulates the logic specific to Prefix treatment of the Search queries related to numbers, and the implied ranges therein.
